n dwarfs and\ndemonstrate the potential of this new instrumental capability for substellar\nastronomy.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 2 Aug 2005 22:52:23 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 12 Oct 2005 07:46:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-13"}
