.9 km/s). However, we find evidence\nthat the difference is caused by a systematic error in data reduction in the\nprevious study, rather than by gravitational effects of an invisible third\ncomponent.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 3 Aug 2005 00:53:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-13"}
